<h1>J2ME Configurations</h1>
<hr /></center>
<ul>
	<li>
	<h2 align="left"><font size="5">Connected Limited Devices Configuration</font></h2>
	<ul>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">CLDC</font></p></li>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">Processor: 16 bit/16 MHz or higher </font>
		</p></li>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">Memory: 160-512 KB of total memory available</font></p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">Power: Limited power, often battery powered 
		operation </font></p></li>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">Networking: Connectivity to some kind of 
		network, usually with limited bandwidth<br>
&nbsp;</font></p></li>
	</ul></li>
	<li>
	<p align="left"><font size="5">CLDC virtual machines omitted certain virtual 
	machine features like floating point numbers<br>
&nbsp;</font></li>
	<li>
	<p align="left"><font size="5">CLDC class libraries not directly related in 
	interface or design to the J2SE class libraries<br>
&nbsp;</font></li>
	<li>
	<p align="left"><font size="5">Certain items of J2SE core library support 
	not present:</font><ul>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">class reflection</font></li>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">thread groups</font></li>
		<li>
		<p align="left"><font size="5">application-defined class loading</font></li>
	</ul></li>
</ul>

